choices are
available. And that can be done
through legislation

21:20.079 --> 21:24.683 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in terms of content of food,
through taxation,
as you have mentioned. These are
important

21:24.717 --> 21:27.019 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
measures that can work.

21:27.052 --> 21:33.058 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then we need to also think
about our urban
planning, for example. One of
the causes to

21:33.092 --> 21:40.032 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
overweight is urbanization.
