walk and cycle safely anymore to
work or to

21:40.065 --> 21:46.338 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
school. And making sure our
cities are healthy
and provide opportunities for
safe walking,

21:46.372 --> 21:49.041 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
cycling, physical activity in
general is extremely
important.

21:49.074 --> 21:52.678 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
