floods are spectacular
and they're global.

24:37.876 --> 24:42.014 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Here's what makes
an El Nino
tick: Normally, trade winds blow
from the

24:42.047 --> 24:47.953 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
