east.

25:03.035 --> 25:09.108 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
BILL PATZERT: So, it's a
tremendous redistribution
of heat. And so when this
happens, all the

25:09.141 --> 25:11.710 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
