rearranged.

25:11.744 --> 25:16.615 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: The unusually
warm water adds
heat and moisture to the air
above it, and

25:16.648 --> 25:21.887 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
