25:41.473 --> 25:46.111 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MILES O'BRIEN: Strong El Nino
winds bring
colder temperatures and more
rain across the

25:46.145 --> 25:53.552 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
