38:48.126 --> 38:51.563 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We will be coming back to this
discussion
many, many times again.

38:51.596 --> 38:56.568 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Thank you very much.

38:56.601 --> 39:01.573 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HISHAM MELHEM: Thank you.

39:01.606 --> 39:09.347 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Next, we begin a
