Agents for
Change.

39:24.729 --> 39:32.036 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: The big
malls may have
arrived, but in India, food,
clothing and

39:32.070 --> 39:36.407 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
