39:49.587 --> 39:55.693 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
SUMIT GANGULY, Indiana
University: Ninety
percent of the work force in
India is in the

39:55.727 --> 39:57.528 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
