39:57.562 --> 40:02.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: That could
be a technical
term that means a very hard
life. They live

40:02.233 --> 40:07.071 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
from day to day. That is, if
there's work
on any given day, they are paid
at the end

40:07.105 --> 40:09.807 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of it, less than $2 for most of
them.

40:09.841 --> 40:15.146 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SUMIT GANGULY: These are people
who have no
Social Security provisions, who
have no health

40:15.179 --> 40:22.587 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
care provisions, who can be
hired and fired
at will. And yet, according to a
recent Credit

40:22.620 --> 40:30.628 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Suisse study, it's close to --
they contribute
close to 50 percent of India's
gross national

40:30.662 --> 40:32.630 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
product.

40:32.664 --> 40:37.268 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Not only are
they underappreciated,
but they fall easy prey to
corrupt officials.

40:37.302 --> 40:42.573 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The market outside of Delhi's
main mosque
has been here for more than 200
years. The

40:42.607 --> 40:47.578 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
vendors complain that they're
subject to regular
harassment from police demanding
bribes or

40:47.612 --> 40:51.382 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
from municipal authorities who
conduct regular
raids to evict them.

40:51.416 --> 40:56.688 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
IMRAN KHAN, Vendor (through
translator): They
kicked us out from here in 2014,
citing security

40:56.721 --> 40:58.589 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
reasons.

40:58.623 --> 41:02.860 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Across
India's cities,
vendors like Imran Khan carry
tales of harassment,

41:02.894 --> 41:07.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
sometimes along with their own
video, of stalls
dismantled and merchandise
confiscated.

41:07.398 --> 41:14.105 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
IMRAN KHAN (through translator):
Then finally,
we went to NASVI, to Arbind, and
he said,

41:14.138 --> 41:16.507 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
you have only one option,
straight to court.

41:16.541 --> 41:22.447 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
FRED DE SAM LAZARO: Social
activist Arbind
Singh founded NASVI the National
Association

41:22.480 --> 41:24.315 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of Street Vendors.

41:24.349 --> 41:27.518 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
